        <p>In Centeral Cordoba is a beautiful and elaborate palace, the <strong>Palacio de Viana</strong>. This palace contains historic interiors as well as many patios decorated with mosaics, fountains, and lush greenery. It's highly recommended to book tickets in advance for this palace if you wish to see the interior, although the patios are the main attraction.</p>
