    </section>


    <!-- Almodovar del Rio Castle Dropdown -->
    <section class="destination-section">
        <a class="anchor" id="almodovar-del-rio-castle"></a>
        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Castillo Almodovar del Rio Castle</h2>
        <p>Further west from Cordoba is an imposing 8th century hilltop castle, the <strong>Castillo Almodovar del Rio</strong>. This fortified Moorish-style castle is very well-preserved and contains medieval furnishings. From the castle you can enjoy sweeping views over the area.</p>
        <p>This castle is a very popular tourist destination because of its use as a setting in the famous TV show Game of Thrones. The castle is approximately 40 minutes from Central Cordoba by car or bus.</p>
    </section>



